## 3. Prepare Your Files (Before Upload)

### Photos

* JPG is perfect
* Donâ€™t over-edit (Commons prefers natural images)
* Original resolution is good (no need to downscale)

### Video

* MP4 works
* Keep it uncut or lightly edited
* Sound is fine (train horn = documentary value)

Rename files clearly *before upload*:

* `Diesel_train_hills_region_year.jpg`
* `Swallows_power_pole_rural_area.jpg`
* `Gravel_road_hills_region.jpg`
* `Diesel_train_hills_video.mp4`

Commons filenames should be **descriptive**, not personal.

